{"tid":2456365,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"馬體會隊醫：夏薩特再做手術 生涯或會終結","createTime":"2021-03-22T01:11:22.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-22T07:21:28.000Z","uid":186071,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f97fbd9829da7121bf954a73264ff3c5c08a7d89","tid":2456365,"uid":186071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T01:11:22.000Z","msg":"夏薩特（Eden Hazard）自從加盟皇馬頻頻遭受傷病困擾，而近期他的腳踝傷病再次引發擔憂<br />\n<br />\n來自馬體會的荷西-干沙利斯博士是該方面的頂尖專家。他表示夏薩特再次進行腳踝手術可能終結他的職業生涯。<br />\n　　「夏薩特只是和球隊合練了10堂訓練課，根據我的經驗，他很難今季再回到皇馬的比賽中，」荷西-干沙利斯博士說；「如果一名球員長期受傷後沒有經過嚴格訓練就返回賽場，再次是受傷是最正常的事情。他有些焦慮，他想證明自己是值得的，並想100%貢獻，但他並不在狀態。」<a href=\"https://m.soccer.sina.com.hk/news/article/12834977/1/20210319?cf=fb_hk_soccer&amp;u=peter&amp;st=rAlP35&amp;fbclid=IwAR1WTneqRlboh5kPuodtEZoFhZ9O21zuFDIhFFvJtDWaBHQrNyUrpLKGX1E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.soccer.sina.com.hk%2Fnews%2Farticle%2F12834977%2F1%2F20210319%3Fcf%3Dfb_hk_soccer%26u%3Dpeter%26st%3DrAlP35%26fbclid%3DIwAR1WTneqRlboh5kPuodtEZoFhZ9O21zuFDIhFFvJtDWaBHQrNyUrpLKGX1E&d=Hu0SY4Cx1oodln7cCHpxbf2u4%2BaHFFj7NdFJeB1nj9U%3D&h=77bd200b\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.soccer.sina.com.hk/news/article/12834977/1/20210319?cf=fb_hk_soccer&amp;u=peter&amp;st=rAlP35&amp;fbclid=IwAR1WTneqRlboh5kPuodtEZoFhZ9O21zuFDIhFFvJtDWaBHQrNyUrpLKGX1E</a>"},{"pid":"53d2cc2b4a8b0db8d1de5bef32b1f036d4f3f0a9","tid":2456365,"uid":186071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T01:12:16.000Z","msg":"開錯台<br />\n<br />\n有冇人可以幫我轉返去體育台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34685b216977521cd1497e3e08f74c828edc6be9","tid":2456365,"uid":225540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T01:35:12.000Z","msg":"皇馬又殺一英超巨星"},{"pid":"362824a8ecf51219b620ee14d6c2619d107405d2","tid":2456365,"uid":186071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T05:55:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"091eb